pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `competence` ( `compID` int(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `title` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `hours` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, `provider` varchar(45) DEFAULT NULL, `description` text, PRIMARY KEY (`compID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=20 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `event` ( `eventID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `date_start` datetime NOT NULL, `date_end` datetime NOT NULL, `contact_phone` int(8) NOT NULL, `rolelist_roleID` int(11) NOT NULL, `description` text NOT NULL, `area` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `point_award` int(11) NOT NULL, `shiftManager` varchar(45) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`eventID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=26 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `Interested` ( `UserEvent` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `eventID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `userID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`UserEvent`), KEY `eventID` (`eventID`), KEY `userID` (`userID`), CONSTRAINT `Interested_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`eventID`) REFERENCES `event` (`eventID`), CONSTRAINT `Interested_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`userID`) REFERENCES `user` (`userID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=364 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `passiv` ( `passivid` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `date_Start` date DEFAULT NULL, `date_End` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`passivid`), KEY `userID` (`userID`), CONSTRAINT `passiv_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`userID`) REFERENCES `user` (`userID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=8 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `role` ( `roleID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `compID` int(11) NOT NULL, `title` varchar(45) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`roleID`), KEY `compID` (`compID`), CONSTRAINT `FK1` FOREIGN KEY (`compID`) REFERENCES `competence` (`compID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `role_has_rolelist` ( `rolerolelistID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `roleID` int(11) NOT NULL, `rolelistID` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`rolerolelistID`), KEY `roleID` (`roleID`), KEY `rolelistID` (`rolelistID`), CONSTRAINT `FK2` FOREIGN KEY (`roleID`) REFERENCES `role` (`roleID`), CONSTRAINT `FK3` FOREIGN KEY (`rolelistID`) REFERENCES `rolelist` (`rolelistID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=216 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `user` ( `userID` int(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `firstname` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `lastname` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `phone` int(8) NOT NULL, `address` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `zip` int(4) DEFAULT NULL, `city` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `age` int(2) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(22) NOT NULL, `admin` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL, `points` int(100) DEFAULT '0', `inactive` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`userID`), KEY `zip` (`zip`), CONSTRAINT `user_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`zip`) REFERENCES `zip_postal` (`zip`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=94 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `user_has_competence` ( `compuserID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `competence_compID` int(11) NOT NULL, `userID` int(11) NOT NULL, `fileUpload` blob NOT NULL, `finished` date NOT NULL, `active` tinyint(4) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`compuserID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=177 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `user_has_event` ( `shiftID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `eventID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `role_roleID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `meeting_point` varchar(45) DEFAULT NULL, `shift_start` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `shift_end` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `shift_leader` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL, `completed` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`shiftID`), KEY `user_userID` (`userID`), KEY `event_eventID` (`eventID`), CONSTRAINT `user_has_event_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`userID`) REFERENCES `user` (`userID`), CONSTRAINT `user_has_event_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`eventID`) REFERENCES `event` (`eventID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=42 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

table.name: competence
table.column: Kurset omfatter 140 timer fordelt på teoretisk undervisning og praktisk førstehjelp. Det teoretisk omfatter: anatomi fysiologi, førstevurdering ved traume, undersøkelsesteknikk, hjerte-lungeredning, infusjonskurs, medisinsk dokumentasjon, trage, opptreden på skadested. Den praktisk delen omfatter: sår og sårskader, blødninger, hode, nakke og ryggskader, bevisstløshet, akuttmedisinske tilstander, generelle sykdomstilstander, bruddskader, kuldeskader, forgiftninger, brann og varmeskader, emosjonell førstehjelp og transport av pasienter.
